---
name: v21-native-collection-companions
---

```scalascript
val squares = List.tabulate(4)(i => i * i)
println(squares.mkString(","))

val grid = List.tabulate(2)(i => List.tabulate(3)(j => i * 3 + j + 1))
grid.foreach(row => println(row.mkString("-")))

val repeated = List.fill(3)("x")
println(repeated.mkString(","))
val ranged = List.range(2, 6)
println(ranged.mkString(","))

val generated = Array.tabulate(3)(i => i + 10)
println(generated(0))
println(generated(2))

val filled = Array.fill(2)(7)
println(filled(1))
```
